{"tid":1467701,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"網上聯署：要求葵涌廣場停止播放無線新聞","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T14:28:43.000Z","uid":288585,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c546328d6d308fd9c80931ce8294099b51601175","tid":1467701,"uid":288585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"葵涌廣場作為潮流指標，一向受青年人熱愛，卻一直於正門的大電視播放無線新聞台 (頻道83) ，使出入的巿民只能接觸單一並偏頗的資訊，對此我們青葵區居民深感遺憾。我們促請葵涌廣場尊重廣大巿民利益，停止播放無線新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c3f15aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(尋晚出咗呢個聯署之後, 今日馬上聽到有組織提議去葵廣集會抗議佢播CCTVB。呢個聯署係手足自發, 為咗唔被騎劫, 希望大家可以馬上就去簽, 讓我哋可以盡快發出公開信俾葵涌廣場!!! 🙏🏼)"},{"pid":"be8e84ce1ee3f15d65ccf6b58d908007eb4a837f","tid":1467701,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:30:37.000Z","msg":"拎遙控去仲好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49846150bca8f5cf24822eedabe0d0bf7e15d572","tid":1467701,"uid":36158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"上次見有人拎遙控轉左個起哂格既台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c704862318601538e5456f15bbe71fad73054a27","tid":1467701,"uid":288585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:32.000Z","msg":"個電視係咁嘅樣，冇得用遙控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ryENKyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FryENKyy.jpg&h=c6654437&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"488939d212d960f8e08e8cd39c4db486c3fce570","tid":1467701,"uid":266916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"由於簽名踴躍, 我哋已經將第一批二百幾個簽名嘅聯署信嚮8月14日凌晨email咗去葵廣管理團隊。<br />\n對方於今早10:56am俾咗一個初步回覆我哋，內容如下 (個人資料遮蔽)：<br />\n<br />\n『致各葵青區居民：<br />\n<br />\n感謝  閣下之電郵查詢，內容敬悉。我們現正處理有關個案並會儘快回覆。有關此個案之所有個人資料將絶對保密。在此期間，倘因個案情況複雜而需進一步調查，我們將適時回覆  閣下有關跟進情況。<br />\n倘有任何垂詢，煩請致電24XX XXXX與XXX小姐聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n南豐物業管理<br />\nXXX 謹啓』<br />\n<br />\n雖然對方似乎已經開始處理，但係簽名唔好俾佢停, 假如葵涌廣場冇進一步回應訴求, 我哋會每隔幾日將新嘅簽名數字再送去俾佢地。<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c3f15aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a>"},{"pid":"737a192d17d9c5878df167bba1951385022afdbb","tid":1467701,"uid":288585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T16:35:51.000Z","msg":"今日4:37PM再收到葵涌廣場嘅進一步回覆，內容如下：<br />\n<br />\n『致各葵青區居民：<br />\n<br />\n感謝各居民之電郵，就葵涌廣場正門電視裝置播放安排之反映，現謹覆如下：<br />\n<br />\n查有關電視裝置並非由葵涌廣場所持有，客戶服務中心於接獲有關意見後，已隨即轉介予負責之廣告公司。經協調後，該電視裝置已停止播放有關新聞節目，並待檢討後再進一步跟進轉播其他媒體之意見。<br />\n<br />\n再次感謝各居民對葵涌廣場提供之寶貴意見及支持，如對上述事宜有其他查詢，歡迎致電2494 XXXX與本客戶服務中心職員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n葵涌廣場客戶服務中心』<br />\n<br />\n以今日嘅兩個回覆嚟講，葵涌廣場嘅回覆效率及相應行動應該可以讓大部分人滿意及接受。因此，我哋稍後會回覆俾葵涌廣場，多謝佢哋咁快做嘢，同時我哋要重申我哋唔要CCTVB。跟住我哋會繼續監察葵廣門口個大電視，希望佢哋做到言之必可行也， 否則我哋一定會繼續跟進。<br />\n<br />\n有進一步進展嘅時候，我哋會再發佈，感謝大家嘅簽署。聯署仍然有效，歡迎未簽嘅人可以入去簽。<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c3f15aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a>"},{"pid":"d7ea1895303dc7fd6240f39453b80f4cd505c040","tid":1467701,"uid":201732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T13:30:54.000Z","msg":"推推<br />\n818<br />\n818<br />\n<br />\n721"},{"pid":"487d6c1cc59c3fbff58a7a5416f9f636ec91fb6d","tid":1467701,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c546328d6d308fd9c80931ce8294099b51601175","tid":1467701,"uid":288585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"葵涌廣場作為潮流指標，一向受青年人熱愛，卻一直於正門的大電視播放無線新聞台 (頻道83) ，使出入的巿民只能接觸單一並偏頗的資訊，對此我們青葵區居民深感遺憾。我們促請葵涌廣場尊重廣大巿民利益，停止播放無線新聞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ij1GN3hMT3pF%2B84p80JiLMiI%3D&h=c3f15aff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc7DSQtIXXML8I3bo0UHSA5WmNSDbZp2BFLkR4Gxq1ffXQWEw/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n(尋晚出咗呢個聯署之後, 今日馬上聽到有組織提議去葵廣集會抗議佢播CCTVB。呢個聯署係手足自發, 為咗唔被騎劫, 希望大家可以馬上就去簽, 讓我哋可以盡快發出公開信俾葵涌廣場!!! 🙏🏼)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:28:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7981df64877cabd4fb4dc0cc699ed1aea21180e","tid":1467701,"uid":289846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"支那再教育營黑幕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1477248/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1477248/page/1</a>"}]}